fimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/focused-inbox-enabled-in-the-outlook-windows-app.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                \u003cimg width=\"1030\" height=\"344\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"Focused Inbox enabled in the Outlook Windows app\" data-img-url=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/focused-inbox-enabled-in-the-outlook-windows-app.png\" src=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/focused-inbox-enabled-in-the-outlook-windows-app.png\"/\u003e\n    \u003c/picture\u003e\n                                    \n    \u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e Focused Inbox uses filtering to prioritize emails based on your past interactions with contacts and important senders. However, you can also manually move emails to the Focused tab. Select and right-click the email you want to move, choose \u003cstrong\u003eMove\u003c/strong\u003e, then select \u003cstrong\u003eFocused\u003c/strong\u003e or \u003cstrong\u003eOther\u003c/strong\u003e, depending on where you want to send the email.\u003c/p\u003e    \u003ch2 id=\"quick-steps-in-outlook\"\u003e\n            \u003cspan\u003e4 \u003c/span\u003e\n        \u003cspan\u003e\n                            Quick Steps in Outlook\n                    \u003c/span\u003e\n       \u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eQuick Steps in Outlook helps you manage emails faster by applying multiple actions with a single click. For example, you can create a Quick Step to forward emails from a specific sender to your team lead and move them to a folder at the same time. You can also set up keyboard shortcuts for even quicker access.\u003c/p\u003e    \n                \n    \n    \n    \n                \n    \n                \n        \n                                                            \n                                                                                                                        \n                            \n    \n    \n    \u003cdiv data-img-url=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/create-quick-step-outlook-windows.jpg\" data-modal-id=\"single-image-modal\" data-modal-container-id=\"single-image-modal-container\" data-img-caption=\"\u0026#34;\u0026#34;\"\u003e\n\n            \n\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\n        \u003cpicture\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 1024px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/create-quick-step-outlook-windows.jpg?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=1\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/create-quick-step-outlook-windows.jpg?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=1\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/create-quick-step-outlook-windows.jpg?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=1\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/create-quick-step-outlook-windows.jpg?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=1\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 481px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/create-quick-step-outlook-windows.jpg?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=1\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/create-quick-step-outlook-windows.jpg?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=1\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 0px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/create-quick-step-outlook-windows.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/create-quick-step-outlook-windows.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                \u003cimg width=\"1200\" height=\"600\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"creating a quick step in Outlook on Windows\" data-img-url=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/create-quick-step-outlook-windows.jpg\" src=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/create-quick-step-outlook-windows.jpg\"/\u003e\n    \u003c/picture\u003e\n                                    \n    \u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eYou can \u003ca href=\"https://www.makeuseof.com/use-quick-steps-microsoft-outlook/\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eset up Quick Steps in Outlook settings\u003c/a\u003e by using predefined actions or customizing them to suit your needs. You can also create custom Quick Steps for tasks like saving an email as a template for easy reuse. \u003c/p\u003e            \n    \n                    \n                        \n                \n    \n                                        \n    \n        \n    \n        \n                \n        \n    \u003cdiv data-include-community-rating=\"false\" id=\"967a-4063-82f006c73ff3\" data-nosnippet=\"\"\u003e\n        \n        \n                        \t                \n\t\t\u003ca href=\"https://www.makeuseof.com/use-outlook-rules-to-manage-inbox/\"\u003e\n\t\n\t\u003cdiv data-img-url=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/a-person-using-a-laptop-creating-an-outlook-rule.jpg\" data-modal-id=\"single-image-modal\" data-modal-container-id=\"single-image-modal-container\" data-img-caption=\"\u0026#34;\u0026#34;\"\u003e\n\n            \n\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\n        \u003cpicture\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 1024px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/a-person-using-a-laptop-creating-an-outlook-rule.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=422\u0026amp;h=268\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/a-person-using-a-laptop-creating-an-outlook-rule.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=422\u0026amp;h=268\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/a-person-using-a-laptop-creating-an-outlook-rule.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=310\u0026amp;h=220\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/a-person-using-a-laptop-creating-an-outlook-rule.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=310\u0026amp;h=220\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 481px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/a-person-using-a-laptop-creating-an-outlook-rule.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=720\u0026amp;h=400\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/a-person-using-a-laptop-creating-an-outlook-rule.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=720\u0026amp;h=400\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 0px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/a-person-using-a-laptop-creating-an-outlook-rule.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=432\u0026amp;h=260\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/a-person-using-a-laptop-creating-an-outlook-rule.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=432\u0026amp;h=260\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                \u003cimg width=\"2100\" height=\"1400\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"A person using a laptop creating an Outlook Rule.\" data-img-url=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/a-person-using-a-laptop-creating-an-outlook-rule.jpg\" src=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/a-person-using-a-laptop-creating-an-outlook-rule.jpg\"/\u003e\n    \u003c/picture\u003e\n                \n    \u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\t\t\u003c/a\u003e\n\t\n\n        \n                    \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-field=\"label\"\u003eRelated\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\n\n                \n                 \n                \t\n\u003ch5\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t        \t\t\t\t\n\t\t\u003ca href=\"https://www.makeuseof.com/use-outlook-rules-to-manage-inbox/\" title=\"How I Use Rules in Outlook to Manage My Inbox\" target=\"_blank\"\u003e\n\t\t\tHow I Use Rules in Outlook to Manage My Inbox\n\t\t\u003c/a\u003e\n\t\u003c/h5\u003e\n\n                                                    \n                \t\t\t\u003cp\u003eWith the right rules, your inbox can go from chaos to calm—all without lifting a finger.\u003c/p\u003e\n\t\n\n                    \n\n\n                \n                \n                \n                \n\n                \n                \n                \n                \t\n\n\n                \n\n                \n                \n                \n            \u003c/div\u003e\n                \n        \n        \n        \n            \u003c/div\u003e\n\u003ch2 id=\"compare-documents-in-word\"\u003e\n            \u003cspan\u003e5 \u003c/span\u003e\n        \u003cspan\u003e\n                            Compare Documents in Word\n                    \u003c/span\u003e\n       \u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eMicrosoft makes it easy to \u003ca href=\"https://www.makeuseof.com/compare-word-documents-side-by-side/\" target=\"_blank\"\u003ecompare two documents in Word\u003c/a\u003e, though this feature is only available in the desktop version. It allows you to review changes, identify differences, and spot any issues before finalizing your document.\u003c/p\u003e    \n\u003cp\u003eTo compare documents in \u003cstrong\u003eWord\u003c/strong\u003e, go to the \u003cstrong\u003eReview \u003c/strong\u003etab, click \u003cstrong\u003eCompare\u003c/strong\u003e, and select \u003cstrong\u003eCompare Documents\u003c/strong\u003e. In the Compare Documents dialog box, upload both the original and revised documents from your local drive, then click \u003cstrong\u003eOK\u003c/strong\u003e to proceed.\u003c/p\u003e    \n                \n    \n    \n    \n                \n    \n                \n        \n                                                            \n                                                                                                                        \n                            \n    \n    \n    \u003cdiv data-img-url=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/compare-feature-highlighted-in-the-word-app-in-windows-11.png\" data-modal-id=\"single-image-modal\" data-modal-container-id=\"single-image-modal-container\" data-img-caption=\"\u0026#34;\u0026#34;\"\u003e\n\n            \n\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\n        \u003cpicture\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 1024px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/compare-feature-highlighted-in-the-word-app-in-windows-11.png?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=1\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/compare-feature-highlighted-in-the-word-app-in-windows-11.png?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=1\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/compare-feature-highlighted-in-the-word-app-in-windows-11.png?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=1\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/compare-feature-highlighted-in-the-word-app-in-windows-11.png?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=825\u0026amp;dpr=1\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 481px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/compare-feature-highlighted-in-the-word-app-in-windows-11.png?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=1\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/compare-feature-highlighted-in-the-word-app-in-windows-11.png?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=800\u0026amp;dpr=1\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 0px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/compare-feature-highlighted-in-the-word-app-in-windows-11.png?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=1\" srcset=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/compare-feature-highlighted-in-the-word-app-in-windows-11.png?q=70\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=1\"/\u003e\n                \u003cimg width=\"869\" height=\"392\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"Compare feature highlighted in the Word app in Windows 11\" data-img-url=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/compare-feature-highlighted-in-the-word-app-in-windows-11.png\" src=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/compare-feature-highlighted-in-the-word-app-in-windows-11.png\"/\u003e\n    \u003c/picture\u003e\n                                    \n    \u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e Word then merges the two documents and shows the differences as comments in the side panel. If you\u0026#39;re satisfied with the edits, you can merge them into the original document.\u003c/p\u003e    \n\u003cp\u003eTo merge the document, in the \u003cstrong\u003eReview \u003c/strong\u003etab, click the drop-down menu for \u003cstrong\u003eAccept\u003c/strong\u003e, then choose \u003cstrong\u003eAccept All Changes\u003c/strong\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e    \u003ch2 id=\"math-solver-in-onenote\"\u003e\n            \u003cspan\u003e6 \u003c/span\u003e\n        \u003cspan\u003e\n                            Math Solver in OneNote\n                    \u003c/span\u003e\n       \u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eOneNote is a fantastic note-taking app for many reasons. If you\u0026#39;re a student, it can also help you quickly solve math problems or perform calculations.\u003c/p\u003e    \n\u003cp\u003eTo view OneNote\u0026#39;s math-solving capabilities in action, write your mathematical expression or equation without spaces, followed by an equal sign to get the answer. For example, type \u003cstrong\u003e(25+75)/2=\u003c/strong\u003e and press \u003cstrong\u003eEnter \u003c/strong\u003eto view the solution.\u003c/p\u003e    \n\u003cp\u003eOneNote can handle basic arithmetic, algebra, and even some more complex equations. If you have a Microsoft Work or School account, you can also access the Math Assistant feature for more advanced calculations.\u003c/p\u003e    \u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
